# FIXME build fails: BaconQrCode
# FIXME current build fails: vpn-lib-common
# FIXME depends vpn-user-portal (php-bacon-qr-code)
# FIXME php-otp-verifier packaged
# FIXME php-sqlite-migrate packaged
# FIXME otp is being replaced by php-otp-verifier: not yet tested
